[[File:Politico_vending_box_DC.jpg|thumb]]的《政客》自助售报箱]]
截至2017年，《政客》美国站月均访问量达2600万次，欧洲站突破150万次<ref>{{Cite news |date=2017-03-27 |title=Politico Facts |work=Politico |url=https://www.politico.com/about/press/facts |accessdate=2020-11-23 |archive-date=2016-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160918224848/https://www.politico.com/about/press/facts }}</ref>。根据{{tsl|en|Knight Foundation|骑士基金会}}2020年的一项研究，政客的读者多为{{tsl|en|moderate|温和派}}和[[左派|左派]]<ref>{{Cite web |date=2020-11-09 |title=American Views 2020: Trust, Media and Democracy |url=https://knightfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/American-Views-2020-Trust-Media-and-Democracy.pdf |url-status=live |website=Knight Foundation |page=57 |access-date=2022-05-07 |archive-date=2021-05-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210529212826/https://knightfoundation.org/wp-content/uploads/2020/08/American-Views-2020-Trust-Media-and-Democracy.pdf }}</ref>。政客被[[阿克塞爾·斯普林格集團|阿克塞爾·斯普林格集團]]收购后，《[[国土报|国土报]]》和{{tsl|en|Fairness & Accuracy in Reporting|公平与正确报道组织}}表示其员工被要求遵守承认以色列合法性的政策<ref name=":9" /><ref>{{Cite web|date=2021-11-05|title=Politico's Staff Must Toe New Owner's Line—Including Endorsing Israel|url=https://fair.org/home/politicos-staff-must-toe-new-owners-line-including-endorsing-israel/|url-status=live|access-date=2021-12-04|website=Fairness & Accuracy in Reporting|language=en-US|archive-date=2022-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220505123501/https://fair.org/home/politicos-staff-must-toe-new-owners-line-including-endorsing-israel/}}</ref>。

2009年，报纸每期印刷约为3.2万份，在华盛顿及纽约曼哈顿免费派发<ref name="VF">{{Cite news |last=Wolff, Michael |date=2009-08 |title=Politico's Washington Coup |work=Vanity Fair |url=https://www.vanityfair.com/politics/features/2009/08/wolff200908 |url-status=live |access-date=2016-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160414030945/http://www.vanityfair.com/news/2009/08/wolff200908 |archive-date=2016-04-14}}</ref>。国会开会期间，报纸每周最多印刷五期，而到了休会期，每周只出版一期<ref name="WashingtonTimes">{{Cite web |date=2007-01-22 |title=Editor sees room for Politico coverage |url=http://washingtontimes.com/business/20070121-102604-6082r.htm |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231256/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2007/jan/21/20070121-102604-6082r/ |archive-date=2016-03-03 |access-date=2016-05-10 |website=The Washington Times}}</ref>。除了刊登行业协会的整版广告，报纸还列出华盛顿地区政治岗位的招聘启事。

此外，网站还和多家新闻媒体机构合作报道，联合发布视频、印刷及音频内容。合作方包括[[CBS新闻|CBS新闻]]<ref>{{Cite news |last=Johnson |first=Caitlin |date=2007-01-21 |title=The Politico Roundtable |publisher=CBS News |url=http://www.cbsnews.com/stories/2007/01/21/ftn/main2381362.shtml |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160308042511/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/the-politico-roundtable/ |archive-date=2016-03-08}}</ref>、ABC旗下的{{tsl|en|WJLA-TV|WJLA-TV}}及有线电视频道{{tsl|en|NewsChannel 8|NewsChannel 8}}（在卖给[[辛克莱广播集团|辛克莱广播集团]]之前，两者均由{{tsl|en|Allbritton Communications|奥尔布里顿传媒}}持有<ref name="washingtonian" />）、电台{{tsl|en|WTOP-FM|WTOP-FM}}<ref name="InternationalHeraldTribune" />和[[雅虎新闻|雅虎新闻]]选举报道。

== 影响 ==
外界认为赞扬政客一开始的企业理念，即以独家新闻及大批量新闻的发表为优先，从而影响其他更成熟的媒体作出改变，譬如提高生产速度，改变报道语气<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":4" /><ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite news |last=Douthat |first=Ross |date=2013-08-10 |title=How the Post Was Lost |language=en-US |work=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/11/opinion/sunday/douthat-how-the-post-was-lost.html |access-date=2017-07-28 |issn=0362-4331 |archive-date=2022-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220407091751/https://www.nytimes.com/2013/08/11/opinion/sunday/douthat-how-the-post-was-lost.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite journal |last=Kraushaar |first=Josh |date=June 2009 |title=Online News Leads Presidential Campaign Cycle |journal=Journalism Studies |volume=10 |issue=3 |pages=435–438 |doi=10.1080/14616700902987256 |s2cid=145109555}}</ref>[[Axios|Axios]]和大酒杯新闻的创始员工也来自政客<ref>{{Cite news |last=Smith |first=Ben |date=2021-01-03 |title=They Seem to Think the Next Four Years Will Be Normal |language=en-US |work=The New York Times |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/03/business/media/punchbowl-playbook-capitol-hill-politics.html |access-date=2022-04-11 |issn=0362-4331 |archive-date=2022-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220327015555/https://www.nytimes.com/2021/01/03/business/media/punchbowl-playbook-capitol-hill-politics.html }}</ref>。

2012年，凭借{{tsl|en|Matt Wuerker|马特·伍尔克}}创作的社论漫画，网站获得{{tsl|en|Pulitzer Prize for Editorial Cartooning|普利策社论漫画奖}}。除此之外还获得三个{{tsl|en|George Polk Awards|乔治·波尔克奖}}，包括2014年{{tsl|en|Rania Abouzeid|拉尼娅·阿布扎伊德}}调查的[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]崛起、2019年海伦娜·博特米勒·艾维奇（Helena Bottemiller Evich）调查的特朗普政府放弃[[全球变暖|全球变暖]]计划，以及2020年戴蒙德调查插手{{tsl|en|U.S. federal government response to the COVID-19 pandemic|美国联邦政府对 2019冠状病毒病大流行的反应|美国联邦政府应对COVID-19疫情措施}}的政治势力。

